{
    "@! You're here!": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event1",
    "Okay... I guess I'd better introduce my pieces. Wish me luck!": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event1_sv1",
    "Umm... Okay everyone!": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event2",
    "Thanks for coming to my art show.": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event3",
    "As some of you know, I came to this town because I wanted to draw inspiration from the beautiful surroundings.": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event4",
    "This place really feels like home now.": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event5",
    "Okay. I'm going to introduce my sculptures now.": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event5_sv1",
    "I haven't named this one, yet. She started out as an exercise in human anatomy, but I ended up seeing her through to completion.": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event6",
    "Her expression is intentionally unclear... is she embarrassed, amused, pained? I'll leave that for you to decide.": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event6_sv1",
    "This one's called 'Post-Dimensional Nullspace'. It represents the boundary of human imagination.": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event7",
    "The shape and color came to me vividly when I was in a 'trance state'.": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event7_sv1",
    "I've been calling this one 'Egg Heads'. I wanted to create an animatronic humanoid statue to toy with the viewer's ability to properly attribute personhood to a physical entity.": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event8",
    "And the last one is called 'Wood Sculpture 3'. It's a celebration of my favorite sculpting material... wood.": "Town_53_1700_Leah_event9",
